        <scopecontent>
          <p>Topical Files includes awards and citations he received. A book proposal includes correspondence surrounding his last book, discussing subprime mortgages. There are also two book reviews he authored. The folder Federal Reserve Board contains a few records around the time of his resignation from the Federal Reserve Board. The News Media files give an overview of his entire body of work and include a listing of citation where his work is cited or he is mentioned. Two reports he participated with ate included: one for the city of Ann Arbor about revenue effects from a city income tax, and an economic study for the Major League Baseball League.</p>
